title: Conference Championships Takeaways
itunes:title: Conference Championships Takeaways
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. The guys give their takeaways from the AFC Championship game between the Chiefs and Titans (:54). After, the duo then give their takeaways for the NFC Championship game between the 49ers and Packers (9:04). Later, the pair take an early look at the Super Bowl matchup with the 49ers and Chiefs (18:19). To wrap up the show, the guys preview the Senior Bowl (23:14).
